setup in ubuntu server
=======================

sudo aptitude install nginx daemontools daemontools-run
/usr/local/perl/latest/bin/cpanm --installdeps -nv .
sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/webapp/
sudo ln -s `pwd`/etc/httpd/64p.org.conf /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/64p.org.conf
sudo ln -s `pwd`/etc/init/64p.org.conf /etc/init/64p.org.conf
sudo initctl reload-configuration
sudo initctl start 64p.org

logs
====

 * /var/log/upstart/64org.log
 * /var/log/nginx/64p.org.access.log
 * /var/log/nginx/64p.org.error.log

Test
====

    curl -H 'Host: 64p.org' http://64p.org/

